{
  "video_id": "xgBnYr0_FRk",
  "title": "How to create a world where no one dies waiting for a transplant | Luhan Yang",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12840.0,
      "end_time": 14560.0,
      "text": "Hi everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14800.0,
      "end_time": 16560.0,
      "text": "I would like to introduce you to Laika."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17680.0,
      "end_time": 21880.0,
      "text": "To most of us, Laika is simply a very cute pig."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22800.0,
      "end_time": 29336.0,
      "text": "However, to hundreds of thousands of patients in need of a lifesaving organ"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 29360.0,
      "end_time": 31640.0,
      "text": "Laika is a symbol of hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32960.0,
      "end_time": 36560.0,
      "text": "You see, ever since the 1970s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 36800.0,
      "end_time": 39376.0,
      "text": "when organ transplants became a real option"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39400.0,
      "end_time": 43616.0,
      "text": "for patients with kidney failure and other organ diseases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 43640.0,
      "end_time": 46240.0,
      "text": "organ supply has been an issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 46920.0,
      "end_time": 48816.0,
      "text": "Over the last few decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 48840.0,
      "end_time": 53880.0,
      "text": "the issue only worsened as organ demand has exponentially increased."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 55400.0,
      "end_time": 57696.0,
      "text": "Currently in the US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 57720.0,
      "end_time": 61896.0,
      "text": "there are close to 115,000 patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 61920.0,
      "end_time": 64680.0,
      "text": "in need of a lifesaving organ transplant."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 65519.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67336.0,
      "text": "By the end of my talk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 67360.0,
      "end_time": 71120.0,
      "text": "one more patient will be added to this list."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 72120.0,
      "end_time": 76495.0,
      "text": "Today, about 100 people will get a new organ,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 76519.0,
      "end_time": 79336.0,
      "text": "a chance to start their life anew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 79360.0,
      "end_time": 82336.0,
      "text": "and yet by the end of today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 82360.0,
      "end_time": 84840.0,
      "text": "20 others will die waiting."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 86240.0,
      "end_time": 88735.0,
      "text": "The situation is heartbreaking"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 88760.0,
      "end_time": 91656.0,
      "text": "for patients, for their families"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 91680.0,
      "end_time": 94680.0,
      "text": "and for the doctors who want to do more."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 96000.0,
      "end_time": 97936.0,
      "text": "In some parts of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 97960.0,
      "end_time": 101559.0,
      "text": "the situation also becomes a disturbing social issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 102120.0,
      "end_time": 104960.0,
      "text": "In Asia, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 104120.0,
      "end_time": 108176.0,
      "text": "media outlets reported that desperate patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 108200.0,
      "end_time": 112120.0,
      "text": "are obtaining organs from the cruel black market."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 113600.0,
      "end_time": 119150.0,
      "text": "It is clear that a solution is needed to this crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 119400.0,
      "end_time": 121600.0,
      "text": "Human lives are at stake."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 123160.0,
      "end_time": 126216.0,
      "text": "As a biologist and a geneticist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 126240.0,
      "end_time": 129919.0,
      "text": "it has become my mission to help solve this problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 130758.99999999999,
      "end_time": 135775.0,
      "text": "Today, I am optimistic to say that we are on our way there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 135800.0,
      "end_time": 137000.0,
      "text": "thanks to Laika."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 137600.0,
      "end_time": 139936.0,
      "text": "Using gene editing technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 139960.0,
      "end_time": 145816.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s now possible to exquisitely create a human-transplantable organ"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 145840.0,
      "end_time": 148400.0,
      "text": "that can be safely grown in pigs."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 149920.0,
      "end_time": 154176.0,
      "text": "Before we jump into the incredible science that makes it happen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 154200.0,
      "end_time": 158600.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s have a better understanding what xenotransplantation is."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 159120.0,
      "end_time": 163600.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a process of transplanting animal organs into humans."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 164480.0,
      "end_time": 167495.0,
      "text": "You may want to ask, why pig organs?"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 167520.0,
      "end_time": 172336.0,
      "text": "Because some pigs carry organs with similar size and physiology"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 172360.0,
      "end_time": 173560.0,
      "text": "to human organs."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 174280.0,
      "end_time": 176696.0,
      "text": "Over the last half a century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 176720.0,
      "end_time": 181576.0,
      "text": "pioneers of transplantation have tried hard to make it happen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 181600.0,
      "end_time": 184480.0,
      "text": "but with limited to no success."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 185800.0,
      "end_time": 186280.0,
      "text": "Why is that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 186880.0,
      "end_time": 189640.0,
      "text": "Two fundamental hurdles stood in the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 190240.0,
      "end_time": 193416.0,
      "text": "First is a problem of rejection."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 193440.0,
      "end_time": 197256.0,
      "text": "When our immune system sees a new organ as foreign,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 197280.0,
      "end_time": 198520.0,
      "text": "it will reject it."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 199400.0,
      "end_time": 203720.0,
      "text": "Second, and this one is specific to the organs from the pig,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 204760.0,
      "end_time": 209176.0,
      "text": "every pig carries a virus that is benign to the pig,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 209200.0,
      "end_time": 211856.0,
      "text": "but can be transmitted into humans."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 211880.0,
      "end_time": 217376.0,
      "text": "It is called the porcine endogenous retrovirus (PERV),"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 217400.0,
      "end_time": 223400.0,
      "text": "and this virus has the potential to cause a viral epidemic similar to HIV."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 224280.0,
      "end_time": 229560.0,
      "text": "Without an effective way to address these issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 229800.0,
      "end_time": 234680.0,
      "text": "the field of xenotransplantation has been on hold for more than one decade."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 235600.0,
      "end_time": 239680.0,
      "text": "Little progress has been made, until now."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 241480.0,
      "end_time": 245160.0,
      "text": "Let me share with you how I got here today with Laika."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 246280.0,
      "end_time": 250296.0,
      "text": "My journey started from Emei Mountain in China."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 250320.0,
      "end_time": 254736.0,
      "text": "That is the place well described in a lot of legendary stories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 254760.0,
      "end_time": 257399.0,
      "text": "like the \"Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 257839.0,
      "end_time": 260159.0,
      "text": "That is the place I call home."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 260920.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262656.0,
      "text": "Growing up in the mountain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 262680.0,
      "end_time": 265760.0,
      "text": "I started to have a strong connection with nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 266680.0,
      "end_time": 269736.0,
      "text": "This is me when I was seven years old"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 269760.0,
      "end_time": 273176.0,
      "text": "standing in front of an ancient Buddhist temple"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 273200.0,
      "end_time": 275216.0,
      "text": "with a monkey on my shoulder."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 275240.0,
      "end_time": 278816.0,
      "text": "I still vividly remember how my friends and I"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 278840.0,
      "end_time": 282150.0,
      "text": "would toss peanuts around to distract the monkeys"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 282400.0,
      "end_time": 284720.0,
      "text": "so that we could cross to hike through the valley."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 285840.0,
      "end_time": 287335.0,
      "text": "I love nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 287360.0,
      "end_time": 290216.0,
      "text": "When it was time to choose a field of study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 290240.0,
      "end_time": 294240.0,
      "text": "I chose to study biology at Peking University in Beijing."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 295760.0,
      "end_time": 298256.0,
      "text": "However, the more I learned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 298280.0,
      "end_time": 299599.0,
      "text": "the more questions I had."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 300520.0,
      "end_time": 305560.0,
      "text": "How could our genetic makeup be so similar to animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 305800.0,
      "end_time": 307000.0,
      "text": "and yet we look so different?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 307920.0,
      "end_time": 312776.0,
      "text": "How is our immune system capable of fighting off so many pathogens"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 312800.0,
      "end_time": 315520.0,
      "text": "but smart enough not to attack ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 316280.0,
      "end_time": 318799.0,
      "text": "Questions like this tormented me."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 319880.0,
      "end_time": 322719.0,
      "text": "I know it sounds nerdy, but you know I&#39;m a scientist."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 324000.0,
      "end_time": 329256.0,
      "text": "After college, I decided I didn&#39;t want to just ask the questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 329280.0,
      "end_time": 332440.0,
      "text": "I wanted to answer them, so I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 333560.0,
      "end_time": 337616.0,
      "text": "In 2008, I was lucky enough to be accepted"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 337640.0,
      "end_time": 341176.0,
      "text": "into the PhD program at Harvard University"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 341200.0,
      "end_time": 343280.0,
      "text": "and worked with Dr. George Church."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 343920.0,
      "end_time": 345656.0,
      "text": "While working in Church&#39;s lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 345680.0,
      "end_time": 350360.0,
      "text": "I started to learn and experiment with the genetic makeup of mammals."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 351200.0,
      "end_time": 353455.0,
      "text": "Among all the experiments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 353480.0,
      "end_time": 356680.0,
      "text": "one particular one took me closer to Laika."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 357520.0,
      "end_time": 363455.0,
      "text": "In 2013, my colleagues and I made changes in a human cell"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 363480.0,
      "end_time": 365936.0,
      "text": "using a tool you may have heard about"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 365960.0,
      "end_time": 367496.0,
      "text": "called CRISPR."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 367520.0,
      "end_time": 370736.0,
      "text": "We were one of the first two groups"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 370760.0,
      "end_time": 376135.0,
      "text": "to report the successful use of such a tool in changing our DNA."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 376160.0,
      "end_time": 379680.0,
      "text": "It was an exciting moment in scientific discovery."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 380800.0,
      "end_time": 385136.0,
      "text": "The gene-editing tool CRISPR has two components."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 385160.0,
      "end_time": 388656.0,
      "text": "It has a scissor called the enzyme CRISPR"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 388680.0,
      "end_time": 391360.0,
      "text": "and what is called a guide RNA."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 391920.0,
      "end_time": 396560.0,
      "text": "Think about it as genetic scissors with a microscope."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 396800.0,
      "end_time": 399176.0,
      "text": "The microscope is a guide RNA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 399200.0,
      "end_time": 403216.0,
      "text": "which brings the scissors to the place we want to cut"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 403240.0,
      "end_time": 405256.0,
      "text": "and says, \"Here it is,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 405280.0,
      "end_time": 410520.0,
      "text": "and the enzyme CRISPR just cuts and repairs the DNA in the way we want."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 411720.0,
      "end_time": 414936.0,
      "text": "Shortly after we reported our study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 414960.0,
      "end_time": 420895.0,
      "text": "physicians at Mass General Hospital were intrigued by the medical applications"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 420920.0,
      "end_time": 422496.0,
      "text": "of our research."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 422520.0,
      "end_time": 424150.0,
      "text": "They reached out to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 424400.0,
      "end_time": 428136.0,
      "text": "and together, we began to see the potential to use CRISPR"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 428160.0,
      "end_time": 430760.0,
      "text": "to solve the organ shortage crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 431840.0,
      "end_time": 433455.0,
      "text": "How do we do it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 433480.0,
      "end_time": 436600.0,
      "text": "It is simple, yet very complex."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 438800.0,
      "end_time": 444960.0,
      "text": "We started by making changes in a pig&#39;s cell to make it virus-free"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 444120.0,
      "end_time": 446896.0,
      "text": "and human-immune-compatible."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 446920.0,
      "end_time": 451696.0,
      "text": "The nucleus of that cell is then implanted into a pig egg"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 451720.0,
      "end_time": 454616.0,
      "text": "and allowed to divide into an embryo."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 454640.0,
      "end_time": 459936.0,
      "text": "The resulting embryo is then placed into the uterus of a surrogate mother"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 459960.0,
      "end_time": 462000.0,
      "text": "and allowed to divide into a pig."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 462680.0,
      "end_time": 465400.0,
      "text": "Basically, it&#39;s a process of cloning."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 465760.0,
      "end_time": 469616.0,
      "text": "The piglet then carries organs whose genetic makeup"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 469640.0,
      "end_time": 473240.0,
      "text": "hopefully wouldn&#39;t be rejected by the human immune system."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 474960.0,
      "end_time": 481376.0,
      "text": "In 2015, our team decided to tackle the viral transmission problem first."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 481400.0,
      "end_time": 487575.0,
      "text": "We wanted to take out all 62 copies of the PERV virus"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 487600.0,
      "end_time": 489000.0,
      "text": "from the pig genome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 490200.0,
      "end_time": 494336.0,
      "text": "but at the time, it was nearly mission impossible."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 494360.0,
      "end_time": 495776.0,
      "text": "Even with CRISPR,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 495800.0,
      "end_time": 500616.0,
      "text": "we could only do one or two modifications within a cell."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 500640.0,
      "end_time": 507176.0,
      "text": "The record for number of modifications we can do in a particular cell was five."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 507200.0,
      "end_time": 512439.0,
      "text": "We had to increase the throughput by more than tenfold to achieve that."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 513400.0,
      "end_time": 517550.0,
      "text": "With very careful design and hundreds of trials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 517799.99999999994,
      "end_time": 520295.99999999994,
      "text": "we successfully took out all the virus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 520320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521896.00000000006,
      "text": "broke the record."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 521919.0,
      "end_time": 524376.0,
      "text": "More importantly, our studies showed"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 524400.0,
      "end_time": 529456.0,
      "text": "that we could eliminate the possibility of this dangerous virus"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 529480.0,
      "end_time": 531799.0,
      "text": "being transmitted into humans."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 533800.0,
      "end_time": 537456.0,
      "text": "Last year, with a modified cell and cloning technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 537480.0,
      "end_time": 541320.0,
      "text": "our startup, eGenesis, produced Laika,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 542160.0,
      "end_time": 546640.0,
      "text": "the first pig of its kind born without PERV."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 547480.0,
      "end_time": 551216.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 551240.0,
      "end_time": 555216.0,
      "text": "Laika represents the first critical step"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 555240.0,
      "end_time": 558976.0,
      "text": "in establishing safe xenotransplantation."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 559000.0,
      "end_time": 560896.0,
      "text": "It is also a platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 560920.0,
      "end_time": 563896.0,
      "text": "that we can do further genetic modification on"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 563920.0,
      "end_time": 566120.0,
      "text": "to solve the immunology problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 566760.0,
      "end_time": 571856.0,
      "text": "Since then, we have created more than 30 pigs without PERV,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 571880.0,
      "end_time": 577480.0,
      "text": "and they may be the most advanced geno-modified animal living on earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 578400.0,
      "end_time": 581696.0,
      "text": "We named Laika after the Soviet dog"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 581720.0,
      "end_time": 585400.0,
      "text": "who was the first animal to orbit the earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 585600.0,
      "end_time": 588576.0,
      "text": "We hope Laika and her siblings"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 588600.0,
      "end_time": 593400.0,
      "text": "can lead us into a new frontier of science and medicine."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 595360.0,
      "end_time": 600496.0,
      "text": "Imagine a world where patients who suffer from liver failure"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 600520.0,
      "end_time": 603175.0,
      "text": "can be saved with a new liver"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 603200.0,
      "end_time": 606256.0,
      "text": "without having to wait for a donation"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 606280.0,
      "end_time": 608790.0,
      "text": "or another human to die."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 609600.0,
      "end_time": 613696.0,
      "text": "Imagine a world where people with diabetes"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 613720.0,
      "end_time": 617456.0,
      "text": "do not have to rely on insulin after every meal"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 617480.0,
      "end_time": 621576.0,
      "text": "because we can provide them with good pancreatic cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 621600.0,
      "end_time": 623880.0,
      "text": "that can produce insulin on their own."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 624600.0,
      "end_time": 629576.0,
      "text": "And imagine a world where patients with kidney failure"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 629600.0,
      "end_time": 633280.0,
      "text": "do not have to face the burden of dialysis."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 634320.0,
      "end_time": 638560.0,
      "text": "We are striving to create that world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 638800.0,
      "end_time": 640880.0,
      "text": "a world without organ shortage."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 641720.0,
      "end_time": 645456.0,
      "text": "We finally have the tool to tackle the problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 645480.0,
      "end_time": 647616.0,
      "text": "we could never tackle before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 647640.0,
      "end_time": 650920.0,
      "text": "and Laika is just the beginning of our journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 652400.0,
      "end_time": 655575.0,
      "text": "We have to be very humble in front of nature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 655600.0,
      "end_time": 658216.0,
      "text": "because there are more issues to be addressed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 658240.0,
      "end_time": 659856.0,
      "text": "including immunology"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 659880.0,
      "end_time": 663840.0,
      "text": "and things we couldn&#39;t even anticipate at this point."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 664760.0,
      "end_time": 670896.0,
      "text": "However, it is our responsibility to translate the cutting-edge science"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 670920.0,
      "end_time": 676240.0,
      "text": "into medicine to save the lives of all the patients who are waiting."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 677480.0,
      "end_time": 678736.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 678760.0,
      "end_time": 683600.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 689800.0,
      "end_time": 693295.0,
      "text": "Chris Anderson: I mean, Luhan, this is extraordinary work here."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 693320.0,
      "end_time": 694520.0,
      "text": "Come forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 695640.0,
      "end_time": 700560.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s the next steps here? You&#39;ve got rid of the virus."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 700800.0,
      "end_time": 702416.0,
      "text": "The next steps involve trying to get to the point"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 702440.0,
      "end_time": 706216.0,
      "text": "where a human body won&#39;t reject a transplant."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 706240.0,
      "end_time": 708400.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s involved in solving that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 709160.0,
      "end_time": 711415.0,
      "text": "Luhan Yang: It&#39;s a very complicated process."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 711440.0,
      "end_time": 715896.0,
      "text": "So we need to take out the antigen of the pigs."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 715920.0,
      "end_time": 719336.0,
      "text": "In addition, we can learn a lot from cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 719360.0,
      "end_time": 723536.0,
      "text": "How can cancer invade or circumvent our immune system"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 723560.0,
      "end_time": 728160.0,
      "text": "so that we can utilize the trick of cancer"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 728400.0,
      "end_time": 730376.0,
      "text": "and implement that on the pig organ"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 730400.0,
      "end_time": 733480.0,
      "text": "to fool our immune system to not attack the organ."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 735680.0,
      "end_time": 739550.0,
      "text": "CA: When would you estimate, when do you hope"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 739800.0,
      "end_time": 742400.0,
      "text": "that the first successful transplant would happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 743360.0,
      "end_time": 747240.0,
      "text": "LY: It would be irresponsible for me to give you any number."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 748200.0,
      "end_time": 750320.0,
      "text": "CA: We&#39;re at TED. We&#39;re always irresponsible."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 750760.0,
      "end_time": 752496.0,
      "text": "LY: But we are working day and night"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 752520.0,
      "end_time": 754600.0,
      "text": "trying to make this happen for the patients."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 755440.0,
      "end_time": 758336.0,
      "text": "CA: So not even, you won&#39;t say that you think it could happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 758360.0,
      "end_time": 760736.0,
      "text": "within a decade or within five years or something?"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 760760.0,
      "end_time": 763160.0,
      "text": "LY: For sure we hope it happens within one decade."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 764800.0,
      "end_time": 766160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 766400.0,
      "end_time": 769656.0,
      "text": "CA: So there&#39;s a lot of people here who would be very, very excited at that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 769680.0,
      "end_time": 771175.0,
      "text": "the potential is extraordinary."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 771200.0,
      "end_time": 773616.0,
      "text": "There will be some other people here who are going,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 773640.0,
      "end_time": 774896.0,
      "text": "\"That pig is too cute."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 774920.0,
      "end_time": 779496.0,
      "text": "Humans shouldn&#39;t be exploiting something so cute for our benefit.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 779520.0,
      "end_time": 781960.0,
      "text": "Do you have any response to that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 783120.0,
      "end_time": 784376.0,
      "text": "LY: Yeah, sure."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 784400.0,
      "end_time": 789295.0,
      "text": "So imagine one pig can save eight people&#39;s lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 789320.0,
      "end_time": 792416.0,
      "text": "In addition, similar to human donation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 792440.0,
      "end_time": 795176.0,
      "text": "if we only harvest one kidney from the pig,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 795200.0,
      "end_time": 797960.0,
      "text": "the pig can still be alive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 797120.0,
      "end_time": 801176.0,
      "text": "so we are very mindful about the issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 801200.0,
      "end_time": 805576.0,
      "text": "but I think our goal is just to address the unmet medical need"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 805600.0,
      "end_time": 808296.0,
      "text": "for those patients and their families."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 808320.0,
      "end_time": 811600.0,
      "text": "CA: Plus, no one can say that to you if they eat bacon, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 812440.0,
      "end_time": 813656.0,
      "text": "LY: That&#39;s a good point."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 813680.0,
      "end_time": 815136.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 815160.0,
      "end_time": 817616.0,
      "text": "CA: Luhan, thank you so much. LY: Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 817640.0,
      "end_time": 819880.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}